OL,4,CBaccalaureate amid financial pressures
OL,6,FHowever, after running since 2012, the
OL,7,FEducation Committee says it is no
OL,8,Flonger viable.
OL,10,FWhile it acknowledges "this decision
OL,11,Fwill be disappointing for many
OL,12,Fstudents, parents and staff", it
OL,13,Fexplains the current setup "demands
OL,14,Fsignificant staffing and timetabling
OL,15,Fresources, which cannot be justified
OL,16,Fwithin the current financial
OL,17,Fconstraints".
