OL,3,CGuernsey scraps International
OL,4,CBaccalaureate amid financial pressures
OL,6,FCommittee President, Deputy Paul
OL,7,FMontague, adds: "I personally found
OL,8,Fthis a very difficult decision to
OL,9,Fmake. I had to put aside my own
OL,10,Fexperience of the course and the
OL,11,Ffantastic staff who deliver it and
OL,12,Ffocus on what is truly best for all
OL,13,Four students.
OL,15,F"The reality is that the IB Diploma
OL,16,FProgramme attracts only a very small
OL,17,Fnumber of students at present. For a
OL,18,Fprogramme that is nonetheless resource-
OL,19,Fintensive, this makes it increasingly
OL,20,Fdifficult for us to justify."
