OL,3,CGuernsey scraps International
OL,4,CBaccalaureate amid financial pressures
OL,6,FFunding at Guernsey's Sixth Form
OL,7,FCentre will now be solely directed
OL,8,Ftowards A-Levels from next September.
OL,10,FDeputy Montague says: "This sharper
OL,11,Ffocus will give The Sixth Form Centre
OL,12,Fa clearer identity and will help to
OL,13,Fensure that resources are being
OL,14,Finvested where they will make the
OL,15,Fgreatest difference.
OL,17,F"This decision is not about reducing
OL,18,Fchoice but about ensuring that the
OL,19,Foffering we provide meets the highest
OL,20,Fstandards for all students.
